            There was a moment — a split second that should have been the end — when Star Monreal left this world. No warning. No goodbye. Just silence, then light, then something no human language was built to describe.
          </p>
        </div>

        {/* Star two-column */}
        <div className="reveal" style={{ display: 'grid', gridTemplateColumns: '1fr 1fr', gap: 80, alignItems: 'center', marginBottom: 80 }}>
          <div style={{ position: 'relative', aspectRatio: '16/9', background: '#000', overflow: 'hidden', border: '1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2)' }}>
