            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* JR two-column */}
        <div className="reveal" style={{ maxWidth: 960, margin: '0 auto 80px' }}>
          <div style={{ display: 'grid', gridTemplateColumns: '1fr 1fr', gap: 48, alignItems: 'center' }}>
            <div style={{ position: 'relative', aspectRatio: '9/16', background: '#000', overflow: 'hidden', border: '1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.2)' }}>
              <iframe src="https://streamable.com/e/z3w7cj?autoplay=1&loop=1&nocontrols=1" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowFullScreen style={{ position: 'absolute', inset: 0, width: '100%', height: '100%', border: 'none' }} />
            </div>
            <div>
              <p style={{ fontFamily: "'Cinzel', serif", fontSize: '0.6rem', letterSpacing: '0.4em', textTransform: 'uppercase', color: '#C9A84C', marginBottom: 28 }}>JR</p>
              <h3 style={{ fontFamily: "'Cinzel', serif", fontSize: 'clamp(1.4rem,2.5vw,2rem)', letterSpacing: '0.06em', color: '#F5EDD6', marginBottom: 24 }}>
                He was born<br />to protect it.
              </h3>
              {[
                "JR comes from a small town, but his story was never meant to stay small. Through his mother's bloodline, he carries the gifts of his grandfather — a medicine man, a shaman, a healer. The same energy lives in him.",
                "JR does not need cards to know what others are feeling. There was a woman preparing for surgery on her hand. After working with JR, she canceled the surgery completely. Others have come to him carrying pain, fear, confusion, even illness — and left changed.",
